  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening men, boys and key leaders&#x2019; response to GBV</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project&#x2019;s main activities include: a baseline of targeted areas, work to engage make GBV prisoners, targeted work with men and boys including male parliamentarians, work with faith and traditional leaders to end GBV as well as coordination with the national referral system.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through the project the referral system for survivors at community and national level will be strengthened to become more survivor centred. Faith leaders and their institutions will play a more enabling and faciliatory role to respond to survivors and to prevent Gender based violence. Inmates who have been incarcerated for acts of gender based violence will be engaged with a view to support their reformation.</narrative>
  </description>
